text: 2 years back I found this vid and the song is still very addictive to me till today. And I'm not even a carat backthen. At that time, I only know just 2 of them; Seungkwan and Woozi. But since 2 years back, I always return back here and keep listening, watching and laughing to this 'Yipeuda' version of them. Also at that time, there's still has no intention of mine to study about the members or even want to know every single name of them. And now in November 2021, I'm binge-watching their GoSe episodes and even know half-everything about them cuz I'm starting to study them hehe till I'm nowadays very attached to Mingyu and Wonwoo and sometimes (but always actually hehe) attracted to Seungkwan and Jeonghan. I always going back here at midnight before my sleep just to release my tension and stress watching this again and again, its literally giving me another level of vibes and different feeling when you've already know every single one of them. I'm totally pleasure to be the CaratArmy and 97 liners enthusiastic now hehe
